Package org.anchoranalysis.feature.session

Class SequentialSession<T extends FeatureInput>

Object
SequentialSession<T>
Type Parameters:
T - input-type for feature
All Implemented Interfaces:
FeatureCalculatorMulti<T>
public class SequentialSession<T extends FeatureInput>
extends Object
implements FeatureCalculatorMulti<T>
Calculates features with successively different parameters, taking care of caching etc. appropriately.

All feature use the same InitParams, but successively different {#FeatureCalcParams} sequentially.

Caching is applied only within each call to {calculate(FeatureInput) but among successive calls.

Author:
Owen Feehan
